plyTime":"2018-12-19T00:23:50.000Z","msg":"生日快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6da509ec36939343ed49ba9d11a548626c2256b7","tid":946861,"uid":76026,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T01:41:57.000Z","msg":"前晚我老豆問我生日打算點過，果晚返唔返屋企食飯，同堆有咩節目<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我果陣其陣其實無人約我，不過我話果日唔返屋企食飯，怕比佢知道我原來年年生日都無人同我慶祝，無朋友得自己一個過<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今晚打算自己去据扒之後再去睇戲，之後再拎埋蛋糕🎂反屋企趁屋企人訓哂自己同自己慶祝<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁多位點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e5fc4a0c956248a47ac1ddf89028bc52e70d5f3","tid":946861,"uid":116441,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T01:42:44.000Z","msg":"hi happy birthday"},{"pid":"0959e8b2617274eb3204683dc6072375c08bcd91","tid":946861,"uid":85156,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T01:48:38.000Z","msg":"樓豬生日快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e56729545bc2e1fbda3fbe9148c2108e4604bcc","tid":946861,"uid":19262,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T01:48:46.000Z","msg":"我老豆老母都唔記得我17號生日<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雖然我本身都無咩興趣慶祝生日，但係都有少少sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57a97a8f0e7c98d445916926acba6cc5909501bf","tid":946861,"uid":19262,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T01:49:12.000Z","msg":"Btw 樓豬生日快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e046a6391d2edb0981bfa2eedb1799ef8c5c3c4c","tid":946861,"uid":30324,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T01:49:30.000Z","msg":"生日快樂<img src=\"/assets/face